IDL Astronomy Library Search Page IDL Astronomy Library Search Page This page provides a search of the one line descriptions of procedures in the IDL Astronomy Library including all the http idlastro gsfc nasa gov ftp contrib contrib directories except varosi The search includes procedures from the http astrog physics wisc edu craigm idl idl html Markwardt http www fz juelich de icg icg i idl icglib idl lib intro html ICG and http www dfanning com Fanning libraries and most intrinsic IDL procedures Type in a string procedure name s word s part of a word in the box to search through the libraries Enter a string or several strings separated by spaces here to search the libraries Place a in front of a required string a in front of an excluding string and place double quotes around a string containing a space For example fit spline linear gauss fits header will find all procedures whose headers contain fit but do not contain either gauss or fits header and do contain either spline or linear This search page does not include IDL graphics keywords system variables executive commands operators e g the mod operator or obsolete routines Use the IDL online help files instead Another search page for IDL procedures is available at the http www astro washington edu deutsch idl htmlhelp index html U of Washington Astronomy IDL Page last updated 21 Dec 2000 This page includes a much larger database of public IDL libraries but may not be current with the IDL Astronomy Library For procedures related to solar astronomy also check the http orpheus nascom nasa gov zarro xdoc SolarSoft Library Search http idlastro gsfc nasa gov homepage html Return to IDL Astronomy Library Home Page 
